rigel.plugins.core.buildx.models module

class rigel.plugins.core.buildx.models.PluginModel(*, image: str, buildargs: Dict[str, str] = {}, load: bool = False, platforms: List[str] = [], push: bool = False)[source]

Bases: BaseModel

A plugin to build Docker images using Docker BuildX.

Variables:

  • image – The name for the final Docker image.

  • load – Flag to store built image locally. Defaults to False,

  • platforms – A list of architectures for which to build the Docker image.

  • push – Flag to store built image in a remote registry.. Defaults to False,
